library(tidyverse)
library(kableExtra)

x <- read_csv("output/caste_results.csv") %>%
  filter(adj.P.Val < 0.05) 

gene_order <- x %>% arrange(P.Value) %>% 
  pull(`Gene symbol`) %>% unique() 

x %>%
  mutate(`Gene symbol` = factor(`Gene symbol`, gene_order)) %>%
  arrange(`Gene symbol`, Time) %>%
  as.data.frame() %>%
  kable(digits = 3) %>%
  kable_styling()
